info.report-description: LTE Cell throughput measurement (M8012) measures cell throughput related measurements

kpi_info.title: period_duration (period_duration)
kpi_info.use: Duration of the measurement period in minutes.

kpi_info.title: VOL_ORIG_TRANS_DL_SCH_TB (M8012C0)
kpi_info.use: The volume of originally transmitted transport blocks on DL-SCH. UPDATED: The transmission of a MAC PDU for the first time

kpi_info.title: VOL_RE_REC_UL_SCH_TB (M8012C1)
kpi_info.use: The volume of re-received transport blocks on UL-SCH. UPDATED: A correctly received MAC PDU with retransmission.

kpi_info.title: VOL_RE_TRANS_DL_SCH_TB (M8012C2)
kpi_info.use: The volume of re-transmitted transport blocks on DL-SCH. UPDATED: Th re-transmission of a MAC PDU

kpi_info.title: VOL_ORIG_REC_UL_SCH_TB (M8012C3)
kpi_info.use: The volume of original receptions of transport blocks on UL-SCH. UPDATED: A correctly received MAC PDU by original transmission

kpi_info.title: RLC_SDU_VOL_DL_DCCH (M8012C12)
kpi_info.use: The measurement gives indication of the eUu interface traffic load by reporting the sum of transmitted RLC related traffic volumes on DL DCCH. UPDATED: This counter is updated on the transmission of an RLC SDU on DL DCCH towards the UE

kpi_info.title: RLC_SDU_VOL_UL_DCCH (M8012C16)
kpi_info.use: The measurement gives indication of the eUu interface traffic load by reporting the sum of transmitted RLC related traffic volumes on UL DCCH. UPDATED: This counter is updated on the reception of an RLC SDU on DCCH from UE

kpi_info.title: RLC_PDU_VOL_RECEIVED (M8012C17)
kpi_info.use: The volume of UL RLC PDUs received UPDATED: This counter is updated when RLC PDU is received from UE

kpi_info.title: RLC_PDU_VOL_TRANSMITTED (M8012C18)
kpi_info.use: The volume of DL RLC PDUs transmitted UPDATED: This counter is updated when RLC PDU is transmitted to UE

kpi_info.title: PDCP_SDU_VOL_UL (M8012C19)
kpi_info.use: The measurement gives an indication of the eUu interface traffic load by reporting the total received PDCP SDU-related traffic volume. UPDATED: This counter is updated when a PDCP SDU is received from UE.

kpi_info.title: PDCP_SDU_VOL_DL (M8012C20)
kpi_info.use: The measurement gives an indication of the eUu interface traffic load by reporting the total transmitted PDCP SDU-related traffic volume. UPDATED: This counter is updated when a PDCP SDU is transmitted towards the UE.

kpi_info.title: PDCP_DATA_RATE_MIN_UL (M8012C21)
kpi_info.use: The measurement gives indication of the eUu interface traffic load by reporting Minimum UL PDCP traffic throughput. UPDATED: This counter is updated when a PDCP SDU is received from UE.

kpi_info.title: PDCP_DATA_RATE_MAX_UL (M8012C22)

The size of received MAC SDU data is added to this counter over the measurement period. Retransmissions are included in the counter.

kpi_info.title: ACTIVE_TTI_UL (M8012C89)
kpi_info.use: This counter provides the number of active TTIs in UL, that is those TTIs with at least one UE scheduled to transmit user plane data. UPDATED: This counter is incremented with every TTI, in which at least one UE is scheduled to transmit user plane data.

kpi_info.title: ACTIVE_TTI_DL (M8012C90)
kpi_info.use: This counter provides the number of active TTIs in DL, that is those TTIs with at least one UE scheduled to receive user plane data. UPDATED: This counter is incremented with every TTI, in which at least one UE is scheduled to receive user plane data.

kpi_info.title: IP_TPUT_VOL_UL_QCI_1 (M8012C91)
kpi_info.use: This measurement provides IP throughput volume on QCI 1 bearers in uplink as experienced by the UE. UPDATED: The volume of a data burst excluding the data transmitted in the TTI when the buffer is emptied. A sample for ThpVolUl is the data volume counted on PDCP SDU level in bits received in UL for one E-RAB during a sample of ThpTimeUl. (It must exclude the volume of the last piece of data emptying the buffer).

kpi_info.title: IP_TPUT_TIME_UL_QCI_1 (M8012C92)
kpi_info.use: This measurement provides IP throughput time on QCI 1 bearers in uplink. UPDATED: The time to transmit a data burst excluding the data transmitted in the TTI when the buffer is emptied. A sample of "ThpTimeUl" for each time the UL buffer for one E-RAB is emptied.
